Package: funciVar
Type: Package
Title: Calculate overlaps and enrichment between genomic variants and genomic features or segmentations
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Simon Coetzee
Maintainer: Simon Coetzee <simon.coetzee@cshs.org>
Description: Calculate overlaps and enrichment between genomic variants and genomic features or segmentations. This is done with both a beta binomial test for enrichment and fisher's exact test to generate odds ratios.
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Depends: R (>= 3.4)
Imports: ggplot2, BiocGenerics, methods, GenomeInfoDb, GenomicRanges, IRanges, RColorBrewer, Rsamtools, S4Vectors, SummarizedExperiment, VariantAnnotation, data.table, dplyr, grDevices, pbapply, readr, rtracklayer, snpStats, scales, stringr, stats, utils
Suggests: knitr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
biocViews: Visualization, VariantAnnotation, LinkageDisequilibrium
